    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from a well-sorted suspension and reinforced rear subframe mounting points. All critical maintenance\u2014including rod bearing service and VANOS solenoid overhaul\u2014has been performed to ensure the mechanical integrity of the 8,000 RPM redline. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the visceral feedback and analog engagement synonymous with the M Division's golden era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
