      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained daily driver. The exterior finish remains vibrant and clear, showing only the light, honest character marks consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the seating surfaces are firm and intact, and all interior electronics\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no unusual noises or leaks, reflecting a history of consistent, on-time servicing. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been treated with respect and is mechanically sound, offering a smooth ride and peace of mind for its next owner. Full service records are available upon request.",
