      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a sweet new ride? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for commuting or weekend road trips! I\u2019ve priced it to sell because I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy hand-off to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
