      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example is paired with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for precise lateral transients. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its well-maintained status, the mechanical fundamentals are robust, offering a pure analog driving experience with a linear power band and exceptional chassis feedback.",
